twice upon a time is a 1983 american animated fantasy comedy film directed by john korty and charles swenson .   it is the first animated film produced by george lucas .   the movie uses a form of cutout animation which the filmmakers called " lumage " , involving prefabricated cut-out plastic pieces that the animators moved on a light table .   the film features improvised dialogue and a visual blend of live-action , traditional 2d-animation and stop motion .